(5414, 'Gemzar 200mg i.v. vial', 'جيمزار 200 مجم فيال', '342', '445', 'Gemcitabine', 'Eli lilly', 'Vial', 'فيال', '', 'Antineoplastic', '200mg', 'Gemcitabine is a chemotherapeutic agent used as monotherapy or in combination with other anticancer agents. 
